difficulties:

- easy:

  - 50% damage
  - easy songs only
  - no time limit in singleplayer

- normal:

  - 100% damage
  - easy / normal songs
  - no time limit in singleplayer

- hard:

  - 100% damage
  - easy / normal / hard songs
  - venom
  - 60s time limit in singleplayer

- extreme
  - 200% damage
  - all songs
  - venom
  - 20s time limit in singleplayer
